      <title>MYSQL删除三张表的联合信息</title>
      <link href="/yyds/de05866e.html"/>
      <url>/yyds/de05866e.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p></p><p>如要删除三张表的联合信息，使用MYSQL的左连接方法：LEFT JOIN ON</p><p></p><p></p><p>例如，删除三张表中张三的所有数据：</p><p></p><div class="cnblogs_code"><pre><span style="color: #0000ff;">delete</span><span style="color: #000000;"> student,sc,stu     </span><span style="color: #0000ff;">from</span> student <span style="color: #808080;">left</span> <span style="color: #808080;">join</span> sc <span style="color: #0000ff;">on</span> student.sno <span style="color: #808080;">=</span><span style="color: #000000;"> sc.sno                 </span><span style="color: #808080;">left</span> <span style="color: #808080;">join</span> stu <span style="color: #0000ff;">on</span> sc.sno <span style="color: #808080;">=</span><span style="color: #000000;"> stu.sno                </span><span style="color: #0000ff;">where</span> student.sname <span style="color: #808080;">=</span> <span style="color: #ff0000;">'</span><span style="color: #ff0000;">张三</span><span style="color: #ff0000;">'</span>;</pre></div>]]></content>
      
      
